I also have an alternative option that declares
```ts
interface Vector3Like {
    x?: number | null;
    y?: number | null;
    z?: number | null;
}
interface QuaternionLike {
    x?: number | null;
    y?: number | null;
    z?: number | null;
    w?: number | null;
}
```
And then uses `Vector3Like` instead of `ConstructorParameters<typeof Vector3>[0]` if that is preferred.
